query.sqlstring: select va.videoannoid,va.video_id,va.annotation_id,va.frame_id,a.product_id,va.x1,va.y1,va.x2,va.y2,va.x3,va.y3,va.x4,va.y4,a.annotationpath from fuiszmedia.videoannotation va, fuiszmedia.annotation a where va.annotation_id=a.annotation_id and va.setrecord=1 and va.video_id=75 order by va.annotation_id, va.frame_id
